{"tid":1464832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下機場手足散水，再諗下聽日點做","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:19:54.000Z","uid":45235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69bdc355383d44991f892fe9a98d5dbc2bb5396c","tid":1464832,"uid":45235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"你屌我乜都好<br />\n我覺得人地班狗入黎攞人，攞完肯走咁咪比佢地班仆街走。你地係要撚狗、撚公安都撚左粒幾鐘，乜都撚夠啦。<br />\n點解仲要走去封人地走條路，比人地可以大條道理落車清你場？<br />\n其實由入機場第一日開始都講到明唔勇武，我理撚得你平時幾勇幾前、食過幾多煙都好，塞機場除左係要世界關注，更重要係要令到佢經濟損失、亦都要比出入境旅客知道我地做緊乜野！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家跪求各手足離開，重新尋求聽日/之然既行動方向！<br />\n唔好再有任何手足送頭比啲仆街<br />\n一個都不能少！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"828f261f221fdb9dceef6d1c706d94ac02635fae","tid":1464832,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"27bedc6c91067ad2db5cc70a73153693a94ef615","tid":1464832,"uid":45235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"89b36aba274371e59be5df1508d8b790b827020f","tid":1464832,"uid":45235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"828f261f221fdb9dceef6d1c706d94ac02635fae","tid":1464832,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"點都唔分唔割，唔想再見手足無辜送頭"},{"pid":"d8e1bafd98e3bfc9d1a61d1edc424a9be4284941","tid":1464832,"uid":45235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"求離場"},{"pid":"3663843fc7acdaca7ba0beb5572c1165bfb9c36e","tid":1464832,"uid":45235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"跪求大家離場"},{"pid":"a6aafee92bdab98053